<p>John and Dave have arrived in San Francisco for Macworld Expo and recorded today&#8217;s show from the hotel room. Everything&#8217;s shaping up to be a great show, and John and Dave talk through their experiences and thoughts about it. Then it&#8217;s on to some security certificate clarifications as well as some software featured as Cool Stuff Found. Subscribe today for free and enjoy!</p>
